Create Folder
mkdir ghcr-demo
cd ghcr-demo
Create Dockerfile
Create file:
Dockerfile,
then follow one bye one step
Build Docker Image
docker build -t ghcr.io/harikrishnamahato777/ghcr-demo .
Login to GHCR
keep your github repositry name
keep password where Pat which u create genrate tocken that one
Push Image to GHCR
docker push ghcr.io/harikrishnamahato777/ghcr-demo
Delete Local Image First
docker rmi ghcr.io/harikrishnamahato777/ghcr-demo
Pull Again from GHCRdocker 
pull ghcr.io/harikrishnamahato777/ghcr-demo
Run Container
docker run -p 8080:80 ghcr.io/harikrishnamahato777/ghcr-demo
Open browser:
http://localhost:8080